Package gov.tak.platform.contact

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContactBuilder<C extends IContact,​B extends ContactBuilder<C,​B>>
    Builder class used to construct IContact instances, thus allowing them to be immutable.
    Contacts
    Acts as an entry-point to the Contacts API by providing interface instances.
    ContactStore
    The Contact Store allows core applications and plugins to manage IContacts through the API, as well as register/unregister IContactListeners so that listeners can receive notifications when Contacts are added, removed, or updated.
    GroupContactBase
    Internal implementation of an IGroupContact.
    GroupContactBuilder
    Builder for Android-specific group contacts.
    GroupContactBuilderBase2<C extends IGroupContact,​B extends GroupContactBuilderBase2<C,​B>>
    Builds instances of IGroupContact.
    IndividualContactBuilder
    Builds instances of IIndividualContact.
